{"tid":1285170,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"其實 C AllStar 真係清泉嚟","createTime":"2019-07-04T12:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T05:20:08.000Z","uid":245793,"like":47,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8564c53937dba9f615ece6c6c7ffb10058a99a76","tid":1285170,"uid":245793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyOXWj9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyOXWj9.png&h=df09614a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風雨中我們都在一起💜 &lt;沒有剩你一個&gt;<br />\n曲/編：小彤<br />\n詞：鍾晴 <br />\n監：簡 / 小彤<br />\n唱：C AllStar<br />\n<br />\n曾同笑過曾同喊過的於這裡<br />\n高低起跌每次都伴隨<br />\n當刻哭出眼淚 當你或很累<br />\n請緊記堅信至可無懼<br />\n<br />\n如何洩氣仍無放棄都一起過<br />\n每次沒有剩你一個<br />\n有多番挫折辛苦過後不計甚麼<br />\n要信在最後　獲到更多<br />\n<br />\n活出你　活出我<br />\n靜待望日出新的一季　<br />\n入夜後路上燈始終美麗<br />\n明天　再明天<br />\n不管巨浪哪怕窮途 <br />\n忠於最真自己　才不枉費<br />\n<br />\nphoto by : @vdubl<br />\n<br />\n#沒有剩你一個<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢哋有時係多嘢講 係煩膠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢哋喺呢個時候肯出嚟講嘢<br />\n都算係清泉<br />\n我見cf on仔 king ig 都有表過態出過聲<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得絕望 攰 頂唔到落去嘅時候<br />\n放鬆吓 聽吓啲廣東歌都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69d7be0b04700ee1d3b06563f4dc7c07fde1046b","tid":1285170,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wF8MOUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwF8MOUk.png&h=6fe51bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3accc6707c0321d753803960b3d5972278d5071e","tid":1285170,"uid":141914,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"Jase其實都算有出過Story<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解連登咁唔中意佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b445244a2c60f6401dfb8ef4f417457393c5e56f","tid":1285170,"uid":245793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3accc6707c0321d753803960b3d5972278d507